		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1) Players get close to arguing nobles in the dining room CTY_Main_A -248; 25; -51&#xD;&#xA;2)Interact with any of the nobles, then follow them outside&#xD;&#xA;3) Interact with a noble during the AD&#xD;&#xA;4) End second dialog and have them fight or leave&#xD;&#xA;5) Talk to Noble 1" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="10" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Two nobles in Jannath Estate argue and finally come to blows. This oneliner is for if AngryNoble_001 is the survivor or if both nobles were calmed down. This noble sold the fake painting." />
